node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hannah Teter in Lake Tahoe, California with @hyundaiusa. May be an image of car and road.

node.text:
Every time I come to Emerald Bay a calmness washes over me as I meditate on this amazing life's journey; I love the feeling of being completely present in this adventurous moment. Shout out to @hyundaiusa for the opportunity to spend some time with this 2022 Tucson... I can't think of a better vehicle to get me to this spectacular view. ❤️🚙 

#HyundaiPartner #ItsYourJourney #HyundaiTucson

node.text:
🏄 + 🥾 + 🏂 #3in1 ✔️I had so much fun hanging with this crew! And I got to test out the @hyundaiusa #Tucson’s Snow Mode, which is going to be perfect for next winter. ❄️
Shoutout to @alanarblanchard, @jackfreestone, @lukecarljohn for joining me on this adventure! 
#HyundaiPartner

Limited trim models with options shown.

node.text:
#HyundaiPartner - Have you guys heard of snowboarding + surfing in one day? Yeah, we decided to step it up to a #3in1 with @hyundaiusa !!💪🏼 
Watch as @lukecarljohn @alanarblanchard @jackfreestone and I 🏄🏽‍♂️ + 🥾 + 🏂 IN ONE SINGLE DAY! Swipe the link in my stories to check it out!
